<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: abandoned settlement -->
  <AbandonedSettlement.label>废弃定居点</AbandonedSettlement.label>
  <!-- EN: The gravcore energy signature is coming from somewhere in this settlement. Explore the abandoned buildings to find the gravcore. -->
  <AbandonedSettlement.description>逆重核心的能量信号正从这个定居点的某处发出。探索废弃的建筑来找到逆重核心。</AbandonedSettlement.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <AbandonedSettlement.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</AbandonedSettlement.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: ancient reactor -->
  <AncientReactor.label>远古反应堆</AncientReactor.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient reactor is hidden within nearby ruins. The reactor is cracked and leaking toxic fallout over the whole region. Locate and disable the reactor to obtain a gravcore and stop the fallout. -->
  <AncientReactor.description>一座远古反应堆隐匿于附近的废墟中。有害物质从反应堆裂缝泄漏出来，导致周边地区被有毒尘埃笼罩。找到并关闭反应堆以获得逆重核心以消除有毒尘埃。</AncientReactor.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <AncientReactor.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</AncientReactor.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: ancient stockpile -->
  <AncientStockpile.label>远古仓库</AncientStockpile.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore emanating from an ancient underground stockpile. The location is marked on the world map.\n\nObtain gravcores and gravlite panels to increase the size of your gravship. -->
  <AncientStockpile.description>你探测到了一个逆重核心的能量信号。信号源于一处远古地下仓库。具体位置已在世界地图上标记。\n\n获取逆重核心和逆重板以扩展你的逆重飞船。</AncientStockpile.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <AncientStockpile.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</AncientStockpile.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: crashed mechanoid platform -->
  <CrashedMechanoidPlatform.label>坠毁的机械族设施</CrashedMechanoidPlatform.label>
  <!-- EN: The remains of an orbital platform are strewn nearby. Be careful, the wreckage contains hostile mechanoids.\n\nThe gravcore signal is coming from somewhere within the crash site. -->
  <CrashedMechanoidPlatform.description>附近散落着一座轨道设施的残骸。小心，残骸中有敌对机械族。\n\n逆重核心的信号来自坠毁地点的内部某处。</CrashedMechanoidPlatform.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <CrashedMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</CrashedMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: frozen terraformer -->
  <FrozenTerraformer.label>故障的环境改造装置</FrozenTerraformer.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore. The gravcore is powering a malfunctioning ancient terraformer. Its location is marked on the world map.\n\nThe terraformer is cooling the local region to dangerously low temperatures. Be prepared for cold weather.\n\nObtain gravcores and gravlite panels to increase the size of your gravship. -->
  <FrozenTerraformer.description>探测到了一个逆重核心的能量信号。该逆重核心正在为一处故障的远古环境改造装置提供能量。其位置已在世界地图上标记。\n\n环境改造装置正把当地温度降到危险范围。需为严寒做好准备。\n\获取逆重核心和逆重板以扩展你的逆重飞船。</FrozenTerraformer.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <FrozenTerraformer.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</FrozenTerraformer.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: cave system -->
  <InsectLair.label>洞穴</InsectLair.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore emanating from a cave system deep underground. The entrance to the cave system is marked on the world map.\n\nObtain gravcores and gravlite paneling to upgrade your gravship. -->
  <InsectLair.description>你探测到了一个逆重核心的能量信号。信号源自地下深处的洞穴。洞穴入口已在世界地图上标记。\n\n地下洞穴极其危险，探索可能耗时数天。\n\n获取逆重核心和逆重板以扩展你的逆重飞船。</InsectLair.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <InsectLair.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</InsectLair.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: mechanoid relay -->
  <MechanoidRelay.label>机械族中继器</MechanoidRelay.label>
  <!-- EN: The gravcore energy signature is coming from a mechanoid communication relay here. Disassemble it to acquire the gravcore. -->
  <MechanoidRelay.description>逆重核心的能量信号来自于这里的机械族通讯中继器。拆解它可以获得逆重核心。</MechanoidRelay.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <MechanoidRelay.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</MechanoidRelay.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: abandoned orbital platform -->
  <OrbitalAncientPlatform.label>废弃轨道设施</OrbitalAncientPlatform.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore.\n\nBe careful - orbital locations are extremely dangerous. Ensure your gravship is fully enclosed with airtight walls and equip your colonists with vacsuits. Plan your return trip, as living in orbit for long periods is very difficult. -->
  <OrbitalAncientPlatform.description>你探测到了一个逆重核心的能量信号。信号来自一处废弃的轨道设施。\n\n请注意，轨道区域极其危险。为殖民者配备真空服。提前计划好返程方案，在轨道长期生存极其困难。</OrbitalAncientPlatform.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <OrbitalAncientPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</OrbitalAncientPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: mechanoid platform -->
  <OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.label>机械族设施</OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore on this platform. There is a heavy mechanoid presence.\n\nBe careful, orbital locations are extremely dangerous. Ensure your gravship is fully enclosed with airtight walls and equip your colonists with vacsuits. Plan your return trip, as living in orbit for long periods is very difficult. -->
  <OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.description>你在此处探测到了一个逆重核心的能量信号。扫描显示有严密防御力量。\n\n请注意，轨道区域极其危险。为殖民者配备真空服。提前计划好返程方案，在轨道长期生存极其困难。</OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：逆重核心</OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: mechhive -->
  <OrbitalMechhive.label>机械主巢</OrbitalMechhive.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the mechhive in orbit above the planet. Its location is marked on the world map.\n\nThe mechhive is the center of mechanoid intelligence and directs mechanoids across planet. If shut it down, it will disable mechanoids planet-wide. Alternatively, you may be able to use the mechhive for your own purposes.\n\nBe warned, mechhives are extremely dangerous. Finish exploring other locations first and ensure you're prepared for a long stay in orbit. -->
  <OrbitalMechhive.description>你在近地轨道上探测到了机械主巢，其位置已在世界地图上标记。\n\n该机械主巢是本星球机械族的指挥中枢。若成功关闭，全球敌对机械族将彻底瘫痪；或可将其改造以掌控其力量。\n\n警告：极度危险，请优先探索其他区域，并确保已做好长时间轨道驻留的准备。</OrbitalMechhive.description>
  
</LanguageData>